description: Inission AB engages in the provision of logistics services in the field of industrial electronics. The company is headquartered in Karlstad, Varmland and currently employs 524 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-06-10. The firm develops and manufactures complete solutions or components for the medical technology, automotive, measuring instruments, telecommunication, marine and control technology industries to achieve economic efficiancy throughout the chain, from suppliers to the customer's customer. Inission is active in Sweden and operates five production units located in Stockholm, Gothenburg, Munkfors, Pajala and Tallinn. The company operates through numerous subsidiaries, including Onrox Group AB.
naics: Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing
name: Inission AB
